  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nFeature.\r\n\r\n**What is the current behavior?**\r\nThere is no possibility to catch start/stop pull-to-refresh gesture event of \"RefreshControl\" component.\r\n\r\n**What is the expected behavior?**\r\nWould be great have something like \"onPullStart\" and \"onPullEnd\" event to know the moment of start/stop pull-to-refresh gesture.\r\n\r\nRelated question on [stackoverflow](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/43784388/is-there-a-way-to-catch-start-stop-event-using-pull-to-refresh-gesture-of-listvi).\r\n\r\n![3](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/24571089/25739204/8f773a20-3189-11e7-9aa7-400002a380f1.jpg)",
